name: Feedback Projector
body:
### Welcome to The Feedback Projector Project.
This page will be used to share all ideas, code, and designs related to the project. You can check out the new branch by executing the following commands:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
In September 2014, Kellie Amott (@KelAmo), Brandon Huddleston, and Jack King began this Feedback Projector Project.
